{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"01ce898d13","title":"谢增辉的右派言论","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"088020e14d","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"01ce898d13"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"4c0546f58a","name":"成都工学院"},{"id":"dd89ef9af3","name":"谢增辉"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"119e3ff9fa","type":"title","text":"谢增辉的右派言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"01ce898d13"},{"id":"cc2d98d2a1","type":"authors","text":"成都工学院谢增辉","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"01ce898d13"},{"id":"3f41469b18","type":"subtitle","text":"(谢增辉：成都工学院学生)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"01ce898d13"},{"id":"a4a8e71035","type":"paragraph","text":"“肃反是小题大作，把思想问题当作政治问题。”","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"01ce898d13"},{"id":"27f918297e","type":"paragraph","text":"“狮子滩水电站水库大，是劳民伤财使得很多人流离失所。”","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"01ce898d13"},{"id":"66c0921743","type":"paragraph","text":"“工资改革是明改暗不改，工资增加了，物价又涨。”","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"01ce898d13"},{"id":"9b827cc6e0","type":"paragraph","text":"“我认为中间路线是有的，一个人勤勤默默只为工资工作，不喊口号，这就是中间路线。”","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"01ce898d13"},{"id":"bdfe2f1e45","type":"paragraph","text":"“假使在中国发生匈牙利事件时，开初我只是坐视，后我积极参加跟反动派跑。”","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"01ce898d13"},{"id":"4e46e955be","type":"paragraph","text":"“我这一辈子决定不拿一分钱来买政治书。”","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"01ce898d13"},{"id":"343e4bdb2d","type":"paragraph","text":"“我觉得马列主义批驳不倒是因为它胜利了，假如他没有胜利是能驳倒的，至于胜利是否长的问题，那就是看共产党阻塞漏洞怎样了，一般说来共产党是会阻塞漏洞的。”","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"01ce898d13"},{"id":"a9d71c62f5","type":"appellation","text":"“助教是党团员当的。”","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"01ce898d13"},{"id":"373bde1a83","type":"paragraph","text":"“领导对党团员特别偏爱，对党团外的群众就不够信任。”","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"01ce898d13"},{"id":"ea66b4bee8","type":"paragraph","text":"“黄键全因不是党团员，所以才被分配到水电厂工作。”","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"01ce898d13"},{"id":"77236c46bf","type":"paragraph","text":"“入党入团是政治资本，才有前途：才有特权。”","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"01ce898d13"},{"id":"74b6238aa2","type":"paragraph","text":"“党团员有特权，可以取得好的工作岗位。”","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"01ce898d13"},{"id":"13b1be97a7","type":"paragraph","text":"“党团员是巫教是两面派，对群众说一套，对领导又是一套。”","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"01ce898d13"},{"id":"9de7611ec0","type":"paragraph","text":"“党团员是政治妓女，是政治恶棍、特务、狗腿子，工人是贵族。”","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"01ce898d13"},{"id":"513d1b9241","type":"paragraph","text":"“共产党都是为满足野心而积极的，与国民党员差不多，共产党员是黑心和尚。”","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"01ce898d13"},{"id":"fce74f742a","type":"paragraph","text":"“在解放军中组织叫我入团时我说：‘我不参加任何狐群狗党’。我是国民党员，再入青年团，别人说我投诚。”","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"01ce898d13"},{"id":"2a536b9b63","type":"paragraph","text":"“百花齐放的方针，是聚而歼之的策略。”","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"01ce898d13"},{"id":"2fd4453b9e","type":"paragraph","text":"“新社会没有自由只有平等，而平等也只是表面的，实际上是在对党员与群众之间也并不完全平等。在资本主义可以自由找职业，没有强迫学政治。”“新中国没有言论、出版、集会、通讯自由。”","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"01ce898d13"},{"id":"8827ea6253","type":"paragraph","text":"“军队是专制的，没有自由，没有思想，军人都是呆子，军队训练出来就是残忍无性的。(国民党时有个朋友参了军，后来就疯了。以前叫我打三十支麻雀都不敢，解放后当了两年兵，现在叫我杀人都敢。)”","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"01ce898d13"},{"id":"518bc88151","type":"paragraph","text":"“新社会人与人之间的关系是不友好的，存在着深刻的利害关系。”","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"01ce898d13"},{"id":"c5b2347fad","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《右派言论选集》（中共成都工学院委员会办公室，1957年）。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"01ce898d13"}],"page":{"id":"c82c669526","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"01ce898d13","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}